WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:900000,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:00:08.925 --> 00:00:09.926 position:50% align:center
[gun firing]

00:00:10.010 --> 00:00:11.928 position:50% align:center
[KANTARO gasping]

00:00:12.012 --> 00:00:14.889 position:50% align:center
[gun clicking]

00:00:16.558 --> 00:00:18.351 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:00:18.435 --> 00:00:20.228 position:50% align:center
[NAGIRI snarls]

00:00:20.311 --> 00:00:22.939 position:50% align:center
[screams]

00:00:23.023 --> 00:00:25.817 position:50% align:center
[HINAICHIA] Tsujigiri Nagiri
has appeared in this town.

00:00:25.900 --> 00:00:28.486 position:50% align:center
A vampire with a danger
Level higher than A.

00:00:28.570 --> 00:00:30.822 position:50% align:center
He's been put on
the most wanted list.

00:00:30.905 --> 00:00:33.408 position:50% align:center
We request the cooperation
of the Hunters Guild.

00:00:33.491 --> 00:00:37.954 position:50% align:center
Be forewarned: Tsujigiri is
an extremely dangerous vampire.

00:00:38.038 --> 00:00:39.914 position:50% align:center
He hardens his own
blood into a blade,

00:00:39.998 --> 00:00:42.375 position:50% align:center
which he uses to
slash open his victims

00:00:42.459 --> 00:00:44.461 position:50% align:center
and draws out their blood.

00:00:44.544 --> 00:00:47.589 position:50% align:center
It's a fearsome ability,
but his immortality is scarier.

00:00:47.672 --> 00:00:50.216 position:50% align:center
Using supernatural means,
he's taken his soul--

00:00:50.300 --> 00:00:51.801 position:50% align:center
if you can even call it that--

00:00:51.885 --> 00:00:54.304 position:50% align:center
and separated it from
his body, then hidden it.

00:00:54.387 --> 00:00:57.599 position:50% align:center
As long as that isn't destroyed,
Tsujigiri won't budge,

00:00:57.682 --> 00:00:59.893 position:50% align:center
even if he's staked
or exposed to sunlight.

00:00:59.976 --> 00:01:01.519 position:50% align:center
He's immortal.

00:01:01.603 --> 00:01:04.064 position:50% align:center
Therefore, our main
objectives are to arrest him,

00:01:04.147 --> 00:01:06.149 position:50% align:center
then locate and
destroy his "soul."

00:01:06.232 --> 00:01:08.735 position:50% align:center
I humbly ask you to
help me defeat Tsujigiri

00:01:08.818 --> 00:01:10.904 position:50% align:center
and protect this town!

00:02:43.288 --> 00:02:45.165 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC] Jeez, I wonder
what Ronaldo and the others

00:02:45.248 --> 00:02:47.000 position:50% align:center
are rushing around
for this time.

00:02:47.083 --> 00:02:48.126 position:50% align:center
[JOHN squeaking]

00:02:48.209 --> 00:02:49.711 position:50% align:center
Eh, whatever.

00:02:49.794 --> 00:02:51.338 position:50% align:center
Anyway, you seem to really like
digging holes, don't you, John?

00:02:51.421 --> 00:02:53.465 position:50% align:center
[JOHN grunts]

00:02:53.548 --> 00:02:55.091 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
Hm? What's wrong, John?

00:02:55.175 --> 00:02:56.676 position:50% align:center
[JOHN squeaks]

00:02:56.760 --> 00:02:58.595 position:50% align:center
What's that you found?

00:03:01.348 --> 00:03:05.101 position:50% align:center
Ah, a small coffin?
What's inside it?

00:03:05.185 --> 00:03:07.020 position:50% align:center
A doll, huh?

00:03:07.103 --> 00:03:08.646 position:50% align:center
I could swear
I've run into something

00:03:08.730 --> 00:03:10.315 position:50% align:center
very similar to this before.

00:03:10.398 --> 00:03:12.108 position:50% align:center
I can't remember what it was.

00:03:12.192 --> 00:03:13.985 position:50% align:center
Could I not touch it?

00:03:14.069 --> 00:03:16.529 position:50% align:center
On the other hand, it looks fun,
so I'll take it home!

00:03:16.613 --> 00:03:18.448 position:50% align:center
After all, I'm the type
who can't resist

00:03:18.531 --> 00:03:20.200 position:50% align:center
pushing a button
I'm not supposed to!

00:03:20.283 --> 00:03:21.993 position:50% align:center
[JOHN grumbles]

00:03:27.874 --> 00:03:30.627 position:50% align:center
[NAGIRI]
Hmm...

00:03:35.173 --> 00:03:37.676 position:50% align:center
[NAGIRI]
What? No! It's gone!

00:03:37.759 --> 00:03:39.219 position:50% align:center
My spirit effigy!

00:03:39.302 --> 00:03:41.721 position:50% align:center
How could someone carry it off
in such a short amount of time?

00:03:41.805 --> 00:03:44.557 position:50% align:center
Was it a hunter with
investigative abilities?

00:03:44.641 --> 00:03:45.892 position:50% align:center
[NAGIRI grunts]

00:03:45.975 --> 00:03:47.894 position:50% align:center
[SHINICHI]
Where is that bad vampire?

00:03:47.977 --> 00:03:49.979 position:50% align:center
We'll get rid of it
once and for all!

00:03:50.063 --> 00:03:53.066 position:50% align:center
It's dark and creepy
around here. [yelps]

00:03:53.149 --> 00:03:54.984 position:50% align:center
[SHINICHI]
Hmm? What're you doing, old man?

00:03:55.068 --> 00:03:56.861 position:50% align:center
There's a vampire
alert out right now!

00:03:56.945 --> 00:03:58.571 position:50% align:center
It's dangerous!

00:03:58.655 --> 00:04:00.031 position:50% align:center
[NAGIRI]
You little brats-- Agh!

00:04:00.115 --> 00:04:02.242 position:50% align:center
[GROUP]
Old man!

00:04:02.325 --> 00:04:04.911 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC grunts]
Oops.

00:04:04.994 --> 00:04:08.331 position:50% align:center
[HIROSHI] Look at that hand!
This is that bad vampire!

00:04:08.415 --> 00:04:10.750 position:50% align:center
For real? Let's be
the ones to beat him!

00:04:10.834 --> 00:04:12.043 position:50% align:center
He looks weakened.

00:04:12.127 --> 00:04:13.962 position:50% align:center
But wouldn't that
be kinda dangerous?

00:04:14.045 --> 00:04:16.256 position:50% align:center
We could always just
harass him a little bit?

00:04:16.339 --> 00:04:17.757 position:50% align:center
[GROUP chuckles]

00:04:17.841 --> 00:04:19.926 position:50% align:center
[HIROSHI] All right, let's
cover him with glue and stuff!

00:04:20.010 --> 00:04:20.969 position:50% align:center
[CHILDREN laughing]

00:04:21.052 --> 00:04:22.929 position:50% align:center
[NAGIRI]
Ah! Stop it, you brats!

00:04:23.013 --> 00:04:24.139 position:50% align:center
Get outta here!

00:04:24.222 --> 00:04:26.349 position:50% align:center
Bastards, I'll slash you into
tiny pieces!

00:04:26.433 --> 00:04:27.434 position:50% align:center
[CHILDREN laugh]

00:04:27.517 --> 00:04:29.894 position:50% align:center
[NAGIRI]
Whoa. They're fast.

00:04:29.978 --> 00:04:33.189 position:50% align:center
[NAGIRI] Now... My spirit
effigy is being hurt!

00:04:33.273 --> 00:04:36.443 position:50% align:center
I need to get it back
as soon as possible!

00:04:36.526 --> 00:04:37.777 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
I'm back!

00:04:37.861 --> 00:04:42.073 position:50% align:center
Hey, Ronaldo, I found
this weird thing by the--

00:04:42.157 --> 00:04:46.286 position:50% align:center
Oh, he's not here.
Did he get a job or something?

00:04:46.369 --> 00:04:48.455 position:50% align:center
No matter.
I'll wait for him, then.

00:04:48.538 --> 00:04:50.373 position:50% align:center
[JOHN squeaks]

00:04:50.457 --> 00:04:53.209 position:50% align:center
Would you care for
something to drink, sir?

00:04:53.293 --> 00:04:57.464 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC] A hot milk, please.
Put it on Ronaldo's tab.

00:04:57.547 --> 00:05:00.467 position:50% align:center
[NAGIRI] Good. I can feel
my spirit effigy close by.

00:05:00.550 --> 00:05:03.178 position:50% align:center
Hm?! The Vampire
Control Division!

00:05:03.261 --> 00:05:04.929 position:50% align:center
Damn! She's in the way.

00:05:05.013 --> 00:05:07.724 position:50% align:center
Should I cut her down
and pass through?

00:05:07.807 --> 00:05:09.601 position:50% align:center
[KOYUKI gasps]

00:05:09.684 --> 00:05:11.394 position:50% align:center
[NAGIRI screams]
So hot!

00:05:11.478 --> 00:05:12.812 position:50% align:center
[HINAICHI]
Who's there?!

00:05:12.896 --> 00:05:14.814 position:50% align:center
[KOYUKI]
Did I burn you? I'm sorry.

00:05:14.898 --> 00:05:17.150 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC] No, don't worry;
you just got the doll.

00:05:17.233 --> 00:05:18.276 position:50% align:center
Wipey, wipey.

00:05:18.360 --> 00:05:20.403 position:50% align:center
[NAGIRI screeches]
Owie!

00:05:20.487 --> 00:05:23.615 position:50% align:center
Ouch! My eyes!

00:05:23.698 --> 00:05:25.158 position:50% align:center
Oh, oh, oh! Don't do that!

00:05:25.241 --> 00:05:27.535 position:50% align:center
[HINAICHI yelps] This guy looks
like he's totally hammered!

00:05:27.619 --> 00:05:29.329 position:50% align:center
[NAGIRI groans]
What?

00:05:29.412 --> 00:05:30.830 position:50% align:center
Who are you calling a drunk?

00:05:30.914 --> 00:05:32.123 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:05:32.207 --> 00:05:34.751 position:50% align:center
Pardon. Let me get
this outta the way.

00:05:34.834 --> 00:05:37.420 position:50% align:center
Listen good, lady. My
name is Tsuji--

00:05:37.504 --> 00:05:38.254 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
Hm?

00:05:38.338 --> 00:05:39.297 position:50% align:center
[NAGIRI screams]

00:05:39.381 --> 00:05:40.715 position:50% align:center
[HINAICHI screams]

00:05:40.799 --> 00:05:42.092 position:50% align:center
[HINAICHI] What? Is something
the matter, Tsuji-argh?

00:05:42.175 --> 00:05:44.135 position:50% align:center
Just hang in there, Tsuji-argh!

00:05:44.219 --> 00:05:45.845 position:50% align:center
No, that's not--

00:05:45.929 --> 00:05:47.263 position:50% align:center
That's not my name.

00:05:47.347 --> 00:05:49.808 position:50% align:center
Anyway, please
just leave me alone.

00:05:49.891 --> 00:05:52.644 position:50% align:center
[HINAICHI] Are you feeling sick?
Do you need an ambulance?

00:05:52.727 --> 00:05:54.270 position:50% align:center
[NAGIRI groans]
No.

00:05:54.354 --> 00:05:56.981 position:50% align:center
I don't need one...
because right now

00:05:57.065 --> 00:05:59.234 position:50% align:center
you're the one who needs...
who needs, uh--

00:05:59.317 --> 00:06:00.735 position:50% align:center
The one... Forget it.

00:06:00.819 --> 00:06:03.613 position:50% align:center
You can tell me after
you've calmed down a bit.

00:06:03.697 --> 00:06:06.199 position:50% align:center
No need to pay me.
I found this thing.

00:06:06.282 --> 00:06:07.784 position:50% align:center
Yes, but it's soaking wet.

00:06:07.867 --> 00:06:10.787 position:50% align:center
[NAGIRI growls] Right here,
right now, you and me--

00:06:10.870 --> 00:06:13.373 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC] We could
take off the wet clothes.

00:06:14.374 --> 00:06:15.834 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:06:15.917 --> 00:06:18.962 position:50% align:center
[HINAICHI screams] A-A flasher?
An elaborate exhibitionist?

00:06:19.045 --> 00:06:21.548 position:50% align:center
Oh, my gosh, no!
I'm not really!

00:06:21.631 --> 00:06:23.675 position:50% align:center
What's that little guy
you've got there, Dral?

00:06:23.758 --> 00:06:27.095 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC gasps] Nothing. I mean,
just a little doll I found,

00:06:27.178 --> 00:06:28.471 position:50% align:center
but the clothes got all wet.

00:06:28.555 --> 00:06:30.724 position:50% align:center
Oh, the poor dear!

00:06:30.807 --> 00:06:33.643 position:50% align:center
[NAGIRI]
You bastard. Why the clothes?

00:06:33.727 --> 00:06:36.187 position:50% align:center
I can't move around
as I please like this.

00:06:36.271 --> 00:06:39.274 position:50% align:center
Think! I need some
kind of clothes!

00:06:39.357 --> 00:06:42.360 position:50% align:center
Clothes. Clothes!

00:06:45.488 --> 00:06:46.865 position:50% align:center
[NAGIRI]
Hm? Huh?!

00:06:46.948 --> 00:06:48.825 position:50% align:center
[HINAICHI]
What the hell?

00:06:48.908 --> 00:06:50.035 position:50% align:center
--[KOYUKI, SENYA giggle]
--[DRALUC] This is perfect!

00:06:50.118 --> 00:06:51.703 position:50% align:center
That's much better!

00:06:51.786 --> 00:06:53.163 position:50% align:center
Stop right there!
You're under arrest

00:06:53.246 --> 00:06:55.206 position:50% align:center
for public indecency, buddy!

00:06:55.290 --> 00:06:56.207 position:50% align:center
No, way!

00:06:56.291 --> 00:06:57.417 position:50% align:center
I at least want to be caught

00:06:57.500 --> 00:06:59.586 position:50% align:center
wearing something less
embarrassing!

00:06:59.669 --> 00:07:01.504 position:50% align:center
This lil' guy is precious!

00:07:01.588 --> 00:07:03.506 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO] Where did you
run off to, ya damn vampire?!

00:07:03.590 --> 00:07:05.258 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
Sand!

00:07:06.426 --> 00:07:09.804 position:50% align:center
[NAGIRI] Huh? Over there!
My spirit effigy is right there!

00:07:09.888 --> 00:07:12.265 position:50% align:center
How dare you toy
with me like this!

00:07:12.349 --> 00:07:14.934 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO] Bastard,
what are you playing at?

00:07:15.018 --> 00:07:16.019 position:50% align:center
Nothing!

00:07:16.102 --> 00:07:17.187 position:50% align:center
--[snap]
--Uh?

00:07:17.270 --> 00:07:18.688 position:50% align:center
--[RONALDO] Hm?
--[DRALUC] Huh.

00:07:18.772 --> 00:07:21.107 position:50% align:center
[NAGIRI yelps]

00:07:22.275 --> 00:07:23.735 position:50% align:center
[SENYA]
How was the patrol?

00:07:23.818 --> 00:07:26.154 position:50% align:center
Uh, we couldn't find
Tsujigiri, but...

00:07:26.237 --> 00:07:27.864 position:50% align:center
[SENYA] Well, I'm just
glad you're alright.

00:07:27.947 --> 00:07:29.866 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO stammers]
Okay! Too close! Too close!

00:07:31.034 --> 00:07:33.870 position:50% align:center
That Tsujigiri Nagiri
bastard appeared in Shin-Yoko!

00:07:33.953 --> 00:07:35.121 position:50% align:center
--[NAGIRI groans]
--[DRALUC] No way!

00:07:35.205 --> 00:07:37.207 position:50% align:center
Someone like that
was around here?

00:07:37.290 --> 00:07:39.584 position:50% align:center
Scary! Sand.

00:07:39.668 --> 00:07:42.212 position:50% align:center
Who is this guy anyway?

00:07:46.007 --> 00:07:49.177 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO]
Bosatsu! Come out, Bosatsu!

00:07:49.260 --> 00:07:51.221 position:50% align:center
How's it going, Ronaldo?

00:07:51.304 --> 00:07:52.764 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO]
Well, not good.

00:07:52.847 --> 00:07:55.183 position:50% align:center
He's gotten himself behind
the plumbing somehow.

00:07:55.266 --> 00:07:56.643 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
Huh. Inconvenient.

00:07:56.726 --> 00:07:58.395 position:50% align:center
Before he poops we'd better--

00:07:58.478 --> 00:07:59.521 position:50% align:center
--[RONALDO yelps]
--[DRALUC] Sand!

00:07:59.604 --> 00:08:01.606 position:50% align:center
What's wrong?
Has a vampire appeared?

00:08:01.690 --> 00:08:03.400 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO]
What is your freaking problem?

00:08:03.483 --> 00:08:04.984 position:50% align:center
[HINAICHI]
I came to observe Draluc.

00:08:05.068 --> 00:08:08.113 position:50% align:center
Okay, but why did you come
up out of the floor, moron?

00:08:08.196 --> 00:08:09.739 position:50% align:center
Last time, that idiot Handa

00:08:09.823 --> 00:08:11.908 position:50% align:center
came in my place without
permission, so I thought I'd--

00:08:11.991 --> 00:08:13.410 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO]
Don't tell me you made a path

00:08:13.493 --> 00:08:15.787 position:50% align:center
down there without asking?
What is wrong with you people?

00:08:15.870 --> 00:08:17.080 position:50% align:center
I thought I'd formally--

00:08:17.163 --> 00:08:17.914 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO] Anyway,
what about your other work?

00:08:17.997 --> 00:08:18.790 position:50% align:center
You have a lot of free time?

00:08:18.873 --> 00:08:20.083 position:50% align:center
[HINAICHI]
Mm!

00:08:20.166 --> 00:08:22.877 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO]
Sorry. I went too far.

00:08:22.961 --> 00:08:25.213 position:50% align:center
Long time no see,
beautiful young lady--

00:08:25.296 --> 00:08:26.840 position:50% align:center
Shut up.
I'm disappointed in you.

00:08:26.923 --> 00:08:29.509 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
Sand! Why? What did I do?

00:08:29.592 --> 00:08:30.677 position:50% align:center
[JOHN squeaks]

00:08:30.760 --> 00:08:33.138 position:50% align:center
Anyway, what were
you guys doing up there?

00:08:33.221 --> 00:08:35.515 position:50% align:center
Oh, uh, there's
this neighborhood stray.

00:08:35.598 --> 00:08:37.684 position:50% align:center
Got himself stuck up there.

00:08:37.767 --> 00:08:38.977 position:50% align:center
He always looks
like he's smiling,

00:08:39.060 --> 00:08:40.729 position:50% align:center
so we call him "Bosatsu."

00:08:40.812 --> 00:08:42.939 position:50% align:center
But he won't come out
even when we call.

00:08:43.023 --> 00:08:44.899 position:50% align:center
[BOSATSU grumbles]

00:08:44.983 --> 00:08:47.027 position:50% align:center
[HINAICHI]
Maybe he just doesn't like you.

00:08:47.110 --> 00:08:48.319 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO]
You didn't have to say it...

00:08:48.403 --> 00:08:50.321 position:50% align:center
All right, I'll help
you guys get him out!

00:08:50.405 --> 00:08:52.949 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC] Oh, yeah? You really
must have a lot of free time!

00:08:53.033 --> 00:08:54.117 position:50% align:center
[HINAICHI]
Free time...

00:08:54.200 --> 00:08:57.495 position:50% align:center
Come on. Stop goofing
around. Let's go!

00:08:57.579 --> 00:08:58.580 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO]
What should we do?

00:08:58.663 --> 00:09:00.498 position:50% align:center
Toss a bunch of
lemon peels up there?

00:09:00.582 --> 00:09:02.167 position:50% align:center
[HINAICHI]
Poke him with a stick?

00:09:02.250 --> 00:09:04.210 position:50% align:center
Though, that might
have the opposite effect.

00:09:04.294 --> 00:09:05.962 position:50% align:center
What if we have
John talk to him?

00:09:06.046 --> 00:09:07.714 position:50% align:center
[JOHN grunts]

00:09:09.174 --> 00:09:12.552 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO] John, convince
the cat to go outside.

00:09:12.635 --> 00:09:14.262 position:50% align:center
[JOHN grunts]

00:09:15.263 --> 00:09:16.264 position:50% align:center
[JOHN squeaking]

00:09:16.348 --> 00:09:18.308 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO]
Huh? What's wrong, buddy?

00:09:18.391 --> 00:09:20.101 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC] It looks like
his little back is caught.

00:09:20.185 --> 00:09:21.019 position:50% align:center
--[JOHN squeals]

00:09:21.102 --> 00:09:22.312 position:50% align:center
--[DRALUC] John!
--[JOHN squeals]

00:09:22.395 --> 00:09:24.564 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO]
Ah! Hurry up and pull him out!

00:09:25.565 --> 00:09:28.735 position:50% align:center
Maybe Bosatsu freaked out 'cause
an armadillo just showed up.

00:09:28.818 --> 00:09:31.363 position:50% align:center
Wouldn't it be better to try
and lure him out with food?

00:09:31.446 --> 00:09:33.990 position:50% align:center
I have some leftover
cookies I baked yesterday.

00:09:34.074 --> 00:09:35.825 position:50% align:center
[JOHN squeaks]

00:09:35.909 --> 00:09:37.952 position:50% align:center
He's a cat, not a toddler.

00:09:38.036 --> 00:09:39.954 position:50% align:center
[HINAICHI grunts]
Mm! Bastard.

00:09:40.038 --> 00:09:42.916 position:50% align:center
What... What's in these things?!

00:09:42.999 --> 00:09:45.627 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC] Welcome home.
I made your favorite dish.

00:09:45.710 --> 00:09:48.213 position:50% align:center
[HINAICHI]
Thanks, hon. I'm starved.

00:09:48.296 --> 00:09:50.799 position:50% align:center
[HINAICHI] You little, are you
trying to seduce me again?

00:09:50.882 --> 00:09:53.343 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC] No, I was trying
to lure Bosatsu out.

00:09:53.426 --> 00:09:55.428 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
Hm.

00:09:55.512 --> 00:09:58.348 position:50% align:center
It's prob'ly faster to scare him
and chase him out than lure him.

00:09:58.431 --> 00:10:00.350 position:50% align:center
What if we make a loud noise?

00:10:00.433 --> 00:10:03.061 position:50% align:center
Or we could do this:

00:10:03.144 --> 00:10:05.980 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC] You just want
an excuse to kill me!

00:10:06.064 --> 00:10:09.818 position:50% align:center
You don't have any
respect for my life!

00:10:09.901 --> 00:10:11.027 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO]
Okay, Hinaichi.

00:10:11.111 --> 00:10:12.904 position:50% align:center
You catch the cat
when he's running away.

00:10:12.987 --> 00:10:14.072 position:50% align:center
[HINAICHI]
Leave it to me!

00:10:14.155 --> 00:10:15.699 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC yelps]
Stop! I'm trying to help!

00:10:15.782 --> 00:10:19.369 position:50% align:center
Wait-- Sand! Sand!

00:10:19.452 --> 00:10:21.246 position:50% align:center
Sharp claws! Sand!

00:10:21.329 --> 00:10:22.622 position:50% align:center
[BOSATSU]
Bite.

00:10:22.706 --> 00:10:25.166 position:50% align:center
[BOSATSU hisses]

00:10:25.250 --> 00:10:27.168 position:50% align:center
He's getting killed
over and over.

00:10:27.252 --> 00:10:28.253 position:50% align:center
Purrgatory?

00:10:28.336 --> 00:10:30.922 position:50% align:center
No! Ronaldo, this guy's crazy--

00:10:31.006 --> 00:10:31.631 position:50% align:center
[BOSATSU]
Meow.

00:10:31.715 --> 00:10:33.049 position:50% align:center
Huh? Get him, Hinaichi.

00:10:33.133 --> 00:10:34.968 position:50% align:center
All right. Bosatsu, come here!

00:10:35.051 --> 00:10:36.386 position:50% align:center
--[hisses]
--[HINAICHI yelps]

00:10:36.469 --> 00:10:37.512 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
Get away!

00:10:37.595 --> 00:10:39.097 position:50% align:center
That cat's a vampire!

00:10:39.180 --> 00:10:44.477 position:50% align:center
Aw, crap. Hey, Hinaichi,
are you all right?

00:10:44.561 --> 00:10:46.312 position:50% align:center
I love kitty cats!

00:10:46.396 --> 00:10:47.897 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO]
What's wrong?

00:10:47.981 --> 00:10:51.317 position:50% align:center
Meow, then my dutiful servant,
capture those two rapscallions.

00:10:51.401 --> 00:10:52.986 position:50% align:center
Yes, Master Bosatsu.

00:10:53.069 --> 00:10:54.612 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO]
She's being controlled!

00:10:54.696 --> 00:10:56.406 position:50% align:center
That guy!
Even though he's a cat,

00:10:56.489 --> 00:10:58.575 position:50% align:center
he has the ability
to hypnotize people!

00:10:58.658 --> 00:11:01.036 position:50% align:center
Seriously? He's got
better powers than you.

00:11:01.119 --> 00:11:02.287 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
Silence!

00:11:02.370 --> 00:11:04.831 position:50% align:center
Hurry up and get that
cat away from Hinaichi!

00:11:04.914 --> 00:11:07.584 position:50% align:center
Sorry, Bosatsu!
Please come quietly!

00:11:08.793 --> 00:11:11.004 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
Ronaldo!

00:11:11.087 --> 00:11:12.380 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO groans]

00:11:14.549 --> 00:11:15.842 position:50% align:center
It's no use, human.

00:11:15.925 --> 00:11:18.970 position:50% align:center
You may as well give up now
and become my servant.

00:11:19.054 --> 00:11:22.223 position:50% align:center
Bad kitty, Bosatsu.
Why are you even doing this?

00:11:22.307 --> 00:11:24.059 position:50% align:center
Isn't it obvious?

00:11:24.142 --> 00:11:26.061 position:50% align:center
With my hypnosis,

00:11:26.144 --> 00:11:29.564 position:50% align:center
I will transform all of
humanity into cat worshippers!

00:11:29.647 --> 00:11:31.358 position:50% align:center
Humans will be slaves to cats.

00:11:31.441 --> 00:11:34.069 position:50% align:center
I envision a world where
hu-meow-nity's sole purpose

00:11:34.152 --> 00:11:35.862 position:50% align:center
is to feed its cat masters.

00:11:35.945 --> 00:11:37.530 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO] Man, this cat
has bigger ambitions

00:11:37.614 --> 00:11:38.948 position:50% align:center
than I expected.

00:11:39.032 --> 00:11:40.492 position:50% align:center
[BOSATSU]
So? Meow 'bout it?

00:11:40.575 --> 00:11:43.578 position:50% align:center
If you submit, then I'll let
you pet my soft, fluffy butt.

00:11:43.661 --> 00:11:45.538 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO] Wh-- I don't
wanna pet your butt!

00:11:45.622 --> 00:11:47.540 position:50% align:center
Kinda looks like he does to me.

00:11:47.624 --> 00:11:50.877 position:50% align:center
Go on, Ronaldo!
Hurry up and become a cat lover!

00:11:50.960 --> 00:11:53.505 position:50% align:center
If you do, then, you know.

00:11:53.588 --> 00:11:56.216 position:50% align:center
You'll... think cats...
are cute, or--

00:11:56.299 --> 00:11:57.592 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO]
You suck at this!

00:11:57.676 --> 00:11:58.885 position:50% align:center
[HINAICHI] Shut up!
I'll turn you into a cat lover

00:11:58.968 --> 00:12:00.720 position:50% align:center
even if I have
to use brute force!

00:12:00.804 --> 00:12:03.973 position:50% align:center
Get a hold of yourself!
You're Vampire Control Division!

00:12:05.141 --> 00:12:06.393 position:50% align:center
Damn it.

00:12:06.476 --> 00:12:08.978 position:50% align:center
She's strong. Really strong.

00:12:09.062 --> 00:12:09.896 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO groans]

00:12:09.979 --> 00:12:11.648 position:50% align:center
Hey, you okay, Ronaldo?

00:12:11.731 --> 00:12:12.982 position:50% align:center
Oh, no!

00:12:13.066 --> 00:12:14.275 position:50% align:center
Huh? Agh!

00:12:14.359 --> 00:12:15.777 position:50% align:center
[JOHN meows]

00:12:15.860 --> 00:12:18.780 position:50% align:center
John, were... were you bitten
in your scuffle with him?

00:12:18.863 --> 00:12:19.823 position:50% align:center
[BOSATSU hisses]

00:12:19.906 --> 00:12:22.325 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO screams]

00:12:22.409 --> 00:12:23.868 position:50% align:center
No, not you, too!

00:12:23.952 --> 00:12:27.789 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO grunts]
I love cats.

00:12:27.872 --> 00:12:29.666 position:50% align:center
Oh, come on!

00:12:30.750 --> 00:12:32.877 position:50% align:center
Meow, it would appear that
you're the only one left,

00:12:32.961 --> 00:12:34.796 position:50% align:center
my feeble compatriot.

00:12:34.879 --> 00:12:38.174 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC grunts] How dare
a cat call me compatriot?

00:12:38.258 --> 00:12:40.093 position:50% align:center
It's quite annoying,
but it looks like

00:12:40.176 --> 00:12:42.721 position:50% align:center
my hyp-meow-sis doesn't
work on you friend.

00:12:42.804 --> 00:12:45.849 position:50% align:center
So, instead, I'll capture you
and use you as kitty litter.

00:12:45.932 --> 00:12:47.809 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC shrieks]
Fate worse than death!

00:12:47.892 --> 00:12:49.602 position:50% align:center
One moment, Master Bosatsu.

00:12:49.686 --> 00:12:51.646 position:50% align:center
He may be more useful as a cook.

00:12:51.730 --> 00:12:53.273 position:50% align:center
His cookies were delicious!

00:12:53.356 --> 00:12:55.442 position:50% align:center
It'd be a waste to
just use him as litter.

00:12:55.525 --> 00:12:57.110 position:50% align:center
You do make a good point.

00:12:57.193 --> 00:12:59.362 position:50% align:center
Then, for three days
a week, he'll be my chef,

00:12:59.446 --> 00:13:01.906 position:50% align:center
and he can be kitty litter
the remaining four.

00:13:01.990 --> 00:13:04.242 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC] Would you really eat
food cooked by your toilet?

00:13:04.325 --> 00:13:05.869 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC whimpers]

00:13:05.952 --> 00:13:07.287 position:50% align:center
That's enough impertinent talk.

00:13:07.370 --> 00:13:08.329 position:50% align:center
I've got you, Draluc.

00:13:08.413 --> 00:13:09.831 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
Sand!

00:13:11.875 --> 00:13:13.043 position:50% align:center
How foolish.

00:13:13.126 --> 00:13:15.795 position:50% align:center
Cats already rule this world,
so why fight it?

00:13:15.879 --> 00:13:17.756 position:50% align:center
Hm? A phone?

00:13:17.839 --> 00:13:20.884 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC cackles]
You got carried away, cat!

00:13:20.967 --> 00:13:22.635 position:50% align:center
This is the end for you!

00:13:22.719 --> 00:13:23.553 position:50% align:center
Purr-don?

00:13:23.636 --> 00:13:25.263 position:50% align:center
What did you do, Dral-- Agh!

00:13:25.347 --> 00:13:28.141 position:50% align:center
What was this urgent business
you had with me, Draluc?

00:13:28.224 --> 00:13:28.975 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO groans]

00:13:29.059 --> 00:13:30.518 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:13:30.602 --> 00:13:34.230 position:50% align:center
Ronaldo, if you sleep here,
you're bound to catch a cold.

00:13:34.314 --> 00:13:36.900 position:50% align:center
Wh-Who is this scary man?

00:13:36.983 --> 00:13:40.362 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC] Behold! Fukuma!
He's our lethal weapon!

00:13:40.445 --> 00:13:44.449 position:50% align:center
Autumn Books' young assassin!
His whole body's a battle axe!

00:13:44.532 --> 00:13:46.910 position:50% align:center
Now, Mr. Fukuma, show that cat--

00:13:46.993 --> 00:13:48.411 position:50% align:center
Aww, cute kitty!

00:13:48.495 --> 00:13:50.038 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC shrieks]

00:13:50.121 --> 00:13:52.248 position:50% align:center
I love cats even more
than I love deadlines!

00:13:52.332 --> 00:13:55.043 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC yells]
This is it for humanity!

00:13:55.126 --> 00:13:57.295 position:50% align:center
Meow, you will become
the cornerstone

00:13:57.379 --> 00:13:59.714 position:50% align:center
of my plan to rule
over humanity--

00:13:59.798 --> 00:14:02.258 position:50% align:center
Don't do it! Don't do it!

00:14:04.094 --> 00:14:08.431 position:50% align:center
[FUKUMA]
I can't. I can't stand it.

00:14:08.515 --> 00:14:10.225 position:50% align:center
No cat should ever
have its heart broken

00:14:10.308 --> 00:14:13.103 position:50% align:center
by the indifference of
cold, unfeeling humans!

00:14:13.186 --> 00:14:15.814 position:50% align:center
You are mine now,
and mine alone.

00:14:15.897 --> 00:14:18.900 position:50% align:center
I will do everything in my power
to bring you perfect joy.

00:14:18.983 --> 00:14:21.945 position:50% align:center
I will make a paradise
here on earth just for us.

00:14:22.028 --> 00:14:23.530 position:50% align:center
Now then, let us go

00:14:23.613 --> 00:14:28.118 position:50% align:center
to a place where you will
be treasured for all eternity.

00:14:28.201 --> 00:14:29.411 position:50% align:center
Meow, wait.

00:14:29.494 --> 00:14:31.663 position:50% align:center
My precious plan--

00:14:31.746 --> 00:14:34.249 position:50% align:center
What the--?
What was I doing again?

00:14:34.332 --> 00:14:36.209 position:50% align:center
--[JOHN grunts]
--[DRALUC] Huh?

00:14:39.671 --> 00:14:41.715 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
Jeez, I can't believe a hunter

00:14:41.798 --> 00:14:44.342 position:50% align:center
and Vampire Control
just let that happen!

00:14:44.426 --> 00:14:46.177 position:50% align:center
You're right.
I'm ashamed of myself.

00:14:46.261 --> 00:14:47.512 position:50% align:center
Oh, shut up!

00:14:47.595 --> 00:14:49.222 position:50% align:center
It's not like you were
able to stop him, either!

00:14:49.305 --> 00:14:50.265 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
Hmph!

00:14:50.348 --> 00:14:51.599 position:50% align:center
Pardon the intrusion.

00:14:51.683 --> 00:14:53.601 position:50% align:center
[RONALDO]
Oh, uh, Mr. Fukuma!

00:14:53.685 --> 00:14:55.687 position:50% align:center
Sorry for all the trouble
with the cat and whatnot.

00:14:55.770 --> 00:14:57.439 position:50% align:center
No need to apologize.

00:14:57.522 --> 00:14:59.107 position:50% align:center
So what's in that carrier?

00:14:59.190 --> 00:15:00.775 position:50% align:center
[FUKUMA]
Oh, it's little Bosatsu.

00:15:00.859 --> 00:15:02.944 position:50% align:center
I decided to keep him as a pet.

00:15:03.028 --> 00:15:04.988 position:50% align:center
Really? How's that
working out for you?

00:15:05.071 --> 00:15:06.865 position:50% align:center
Are you hypnotized?

00:15:06.948 --> 00:15:09.409 position:50% align:center
[FUKUMA]
I'm not. He's a very good boy.

00:15:09.492 --> 00:15:11.995 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
Hm?

00:15:12.078 --> 00:15:13.246 position:50% align:center
--[DRALUC] Sand!
--[HINAICHI, RONALDO, JOHN yelp]

00:15:13.329 --> 00:15:15.874 position:50% align:center
[FUKUMA] Bosatsu,
do you like your new home?

00:15:15.957 --> 00:15:18.376 position:50% align:center
[BOSATSU]
Yes, it is the best home.

00:15:18.460 --> 00:15:21.796 position:50% align:center
Thank you for letting
me be your pet kitty.

00:15:27.010 --> 00:15:31.056 position:50% align:center
[sighs] I've completed the
event and gotten all the items.

00:15:31.139 --> 00:15:32.182 position:50% align:center
[JOHN squeaks]

00:15:32.265 --> 00:15:36.770 position:50% align:center
Anyway, Ronaldo's
taking a long time.

00:15:36.853 --> 00:15:38.980 position:50% align:center
He said he was just
going to Vamima.

00:15:39.064 --> 00:15:41.274 position:50% align:center
Is he reading Champion
in the store or somethi--

00:15:41.358 --> 00:15:43.151 position:50% align:center
I have come for you,
Vampire Draluc!

00:15:43.234 --> 00:15:44.569 position:50% align:center
[JOHN, DRALUC shriek]

00:15:44.652 --> 00:15:46.488 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC] Handa! Are you
here to search the house again

00:15:46.571 --> 00:15:47.572 position:50% align:center
under the pretext of
surveillance?

00:15:47.655 --> 00:15:50.200 position:50% align:center
No, fool! I'm off duty today.

00:15:50.283 --> 00:15:52.452 position:50% align:center
If that's true,
then why are you here?

00:15:52.535 --> 00:15:54.245 position:50% align:center
[HANDA]
Isn't it obvious?

00:15:54.329 --> 00:15:55.789 position:50% align:center
Last time,
the two of us presented

00:15:55.872 --> 00:15:58.083 position:50% align:center
a united front together.

00:15:58.166 --> 00:16:02.045 position:50% align:center
Also, you're a vampire
and I am a dhampir.

00:16:02.128 --> 00:16:03.630 position:50% align:center
Do I have to spell it out?

00:16:03.713 --> 00:16:05.674 position:50% align:center
Yeah, I'm not following you!

00:16:05.757 --> 00:16:07.300 position:50% align:center
Give me one, teeny little hint.

00:16:07.384 --> 00:16:09.427 position:50% align:center
Here's your hint:
I wanna hang out!

00:16:09.511 --> 00:16:11.721 position:50% align:center
Oh. Uh, okay.

00:16:11.805 --> 00:16:14.516 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
I've made a strange new friend.

00:16:14.599 --> 00:16:15.850 position:50% align:center
[JOHN squeaks]

00:16:15.934 --> 00:16:18.144 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC] Ronaldo isn't
home yet, so it's just us.

00:16:18.228 --> 00:16:19.270 position:50% align:center
And he can stay out!

00:16:19.354 --> 00:16:21.314 position:50% align:center
I don't want him
ruining my day off!

00:16:21.398 --> 00:16:23.274 position:50% align:center
So, in order to keep
him away from home,

00:16:23.358 --> 00:16:25.985 position:50% align:center
I went ahead and set up
dozens of celery traps

00:16:26.069 --> 00:16:27.112 position:50% align:center
all around this building.

00:16:27.195 --> 00:16:28.154 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
You're not kidding.

00:16:28.238 --> 00:16:30.365 position:50% align:center
He's sent many texts
asking for help.

00:16:30.448 --> 00:16:32.158 position:50% align:center
I get the whole
thing with your mom,

00:16:32.242 --> 00:16:34.077 position:50% align:center
but you don't
mess around, do you?

00:16:34.160 --> 00:16:36.871 position:50% align:center
My mom? Ah!
This isn't about her!

00:16:36.955 --> 00:16:39.040 position:50% align:center
Ronaldo's always been my enemy.

00:16:39.124 --> 00:16:41.793 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC] Oh, yeah, you two went
to high school together, right?

00:16:41.876 --> 00:16:42.877 position:50% align:center
Interesting!

00:16:42.961 --> 00:16:45.547 position:50% align:center
I'd love to hear
about the good old days.

00:16:45.630 --> 00:16:48.258 position:50% align:center
Hah! You're a real busybody,
aren't you, man?

00:16:48.341 --> 00:16:50.552 position:50% align:center
Okay, then. I'll tell
you about his past.

00:16:50.635 --> 00:16:52.429 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC] Whoa, you brought
a projector and everything?!

00:16:52.512 --> 00:16:53.805 position:50% align:center
Weirdo!

00:16:53.888 --> 00:16:56.182 position:50% align:center
Shut up! You're the one
who wanted to hear about it!

00:16:56.266 --> 00:16:58.268 position:50% align:center
Look, I have lots
of documentation!

00:16:58.351 --> 00:16:59.185 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
So, what, do you, like,

00:16:59.269 --> 00:17:00.812 position:50% align:center
carry that thing
around with you?

00:17:00.895 --> 00:17:02.063 position:50% align:center
You wanna hear, or no?

00:17:02.147 --> 00:17:03.231 position:50% align:center
More than anything in the world.

00:17:03.314 --> 00:17:04.774 position:50% align:center
All right, then shut it!

00:17:04.858 --> 00:17:07.819 position:50% align:center
Now, let's begin! Please remain
quiet during the screening!

00:17:07.902 --> 00:17:10.488 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC] Hold on, lemme
just put my phone on silent.

00:17:10.572 --> 00:17:11.906 position:50% align:center
[HANDA]
Let's see, first--

00:17:11.990 --> 00:17:12.866 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
My eyes!

00:17:12.949 --> 00:17:14.200 position:50% align:center
To hook the audience,

00:17:14.284 --> 00:17:16.286 position:50% align:center
I made a slideshow of
Ronaldo's shameful antics.

00:17:16.369 --> 00:17:18.455 position:50% align:center
[DRALUC]
Skip it, please.

00:17:18.538 --> 00:17:21.332 position:50% align:center
Let's hear how your rivalry
got started to begin with.

00:17:21.416 --> 00:17:24.461 position:50% align:center
[HANDA]
Tch. Fine then, if you insist!

00:17:24.544 --> 00:17:26.921 position:50% align:center
It was the first
day of school...

00:17:27.005 --> 00:17:29.591 position:50% align:center
Handa! You wanna
join Vamp Control, right?

00:17:29.674 --> 00:17:31.634 position:50% align:center
Well, I wanna become a hunter.

00:17:31.718 --> 00:17:32.886 position:50% align:center
Let's team up.

00:17:32.969 --> 00:17:34.262 position:50% align:center
[HANDA] You think you
can compete with me?!

00:17:34.346 --> 00:17:35.430 position:50% align:center
Learn your place!

00:17:35.513 --> 00:17:37.974 position:50% align:center
I'm coming after you
before the vampires!

00:17:38.058 --> 00:17:39.434 position:50% align:center
[HANDA]
And so I understood

00:17:39.517 --> 00:17:41.561 position:50% align:center
that he was a man
to be defeated.

